title: Anomus IDO on Scaleswap
body:
The following vote is to provide your opinion on the quality of Anomus as a project and whether an IDO on Scaleswap should be approved in November.

Anomus is a one-of-a-kind alternative to the deterioration of mainstream media. It's a community-governed, decentralized news protocol for users from all around the world. Built by a team of crypto professionals and backed by well-known names in the blockchain space.

Website: https://www.anomus.io/
Whitepaper: https://wp.anomus.io/

5 stars: Exceptional approval rating - clear for takeoff
4 stars: Very strong approval rating - clear for takeoff
3 stars: Good approval rating - clear for takeoff
2 stars: Fair approval rating - flight grounded
1 star: Poor approval rating - flight grounded
